Interface ProcessSelfRequester

All Superinterfaces:
RecordProcessRequester, org.epics.pvData.pv.Requester
All Known Implementing Classes:
InputLinkBase, MonitorLinkBase, OutputLinkBase, ProcessLinkBase
public interface ProcessSelfRequester
extends RecordProcessRequester

A requester to process a record that is self processed. A record that is self processed allows multiple clients to process the record. Each client can get permission to process. The client must implement this interface.
